title: 10 year mystery gift.
body: I still have not received my gift but everyone i know has. I already own the riot kayle skin prior to this event. Might that have anything to do with it?

replies.body: Not everyone will get the gift right away, and it won't be all at once either.  There are a lot of accounts to cover so it's going to take some time, per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang tight until everything is finished being sent out!
The gifts are still being distributed, so just be patient. The 23rd is the final day the gifts will be given, so if you don't receive it by then, you can submit a support ticket.
